        <h3>Design</h3>
        <p class="project-font-grey">A style guide was produced to ensure all design elements meet the standards of SBS. Vector artwork for the app was created to accompany each module. The app uses predominantly corporate colours with highlights of bright contrasting colour to draw the users focus to important areas. To accomodate users of varying levels of computer literacy a tutorial was created using animated gifs to further explain how to use the app.</p>
        
        <p class="project-font-grey">To increase the educational value and to keep users engaged a series of quiz types were developed. These range from Multiple choice quizzes, match the answer, Implicit Association Test (IAT) and slider bar quizzes to mention a few. Where possible quizzes also give detailed feedback on incorrect answers to improve user understanding.</p>
