          <h3 class="text-color">Navigation</h3>
          <p class="project-font-white">The challenge of this app in terms of the navigation was how to allow the user to engage a large volume of educational material without them feeling lost or overwhelmed in the process. To break down the content into manageable sections, modules were created which contain a number of lessons. When the user logs on for the first time all but the first module is locked. When all the lessons in the first module are completed the second module is unlocked and so on until the course is completed.</p>
